reviewText: For a low budget movie, its great. They are a perfect fit for each other in this. You really feel a chemistry between them. And their expressions are great. It's a real funny movie. I actually bought it for my girlfriend. She watches it all the time. I just saw it on TV once, thought it was great, and got it for her because I knew she would like it. If you want to watch a  funny movie that you and your girlfriend can both watch together, but each get something different from it, get this movie. You won't be disappointed.
The story was sometimes funny and sometimes sad(so much lying) but it was mainly just unbelievable and quite contrived. The male character was dislikeable.
Such a cute, unpredictable, delightful movie that me laughing and not wanting it to end....
Very depressing in a very weird ending if I would've known what the movie was really all about I never would've purchased it
